changelog.release_notes:
v4.4 Update Notes:
1. fixed a bug that no response on first generation pebble occasionally;
2. optimization;

v4.2 Update Notes:
1. Weather support automatic location;
2. A new battery indicator is available, Christmas tree, some lights on the tree, the size of the light depends on battery level;
3. Custom fonts support English characters, not just numbers;

v4.1 Update Notes:
1. Three fonts can be set for numbers;
2. Support two weather data sources;
3. Position of battery level percent can be set to bottle's outside or inside;
3. Bluetooth disconnect alert can be enabled or disabled;

v3.1 Update Notes:
1. Added the battery level percent；
2. When the Bluetooth connection is interrupted, the custom text will show an alert, a vibration is also triggered;

v3.0 Update Notes:
1. Added the battery status indicator, you can disable;
2. Weather icon optimization, distinguish day and night;
3. Supports all square display watches (including Classic, Steel, Time, Time Steel, Pebble 2, Time 2);

data.description:
Language Supports: English, 简体中文, España

/* English */
This watch-face displays date, time, week, temperature, weather and battery information on your watch.
[Features]
- Date shows year, month and day, year and month format can be customized;
- Time shows hour and minute;
- Temperature shows current temperature, temperature unit supports °C and °F;
- Weather uses relevant image to show current weather situation, location and update interval can be set, support two weather data sources and automatic location;
- Battery indicator have two style, Water bottle and Christmas tree, it can be enabled or disabled;
- When the Bluetooth connection is interrupted, the custom text will show an alert, a vibration is also triggered，it can be enabled or disabled;
- Background color， foreground color and font can be customized;
- A text line in footer can be customized；For Chinese users, customized text can be replaced to Chinese lunar calendar;
- Compatible with all watch models;

/* 简体中文 */
这个表盘显示日期、时间、星期、温度、天气和电量信息在你的手表上。
[特色]
- 日期显示年、月和日，年月格式可以自定义；
- 时间显示时和分；
- 温度显示当前温度，温度单位支持 °C 和 °F；
- 天气使用相应的图标显示当前天气状况，可以设置所在位置和更新间隔时间，支持两种数据源和自动定位；
- 电量指示器有两种样式，水瓶和圣诞树，可以开启或关闭；
- 蓝牙连接断开后，自定义文本会显示提示信息，并且震动，可以开启或关闭；
- 可以自定义背景颜色、前景颜色和字体；
- 可以在底部自定义一行文本，对于中国用户，自定义的文本可以替换为中国农历；
- 兼容所有型号手表；

